title: 5TTMM - Wear watch face

descriptionHTML:
5TTMM is a designer watchface app for Android Wear devices. Twelve circles segmented in a twelve parts. Each segment represents a five minute period. Full circle stands for one hour. App has a nine colors customization and works in ambient mode. Have a great TTMM.

Compatible with Huawei Watch, Motorola Moto 360, LG G Watch, LG G Watch R, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch 3

Idea & design : Albert Salamon
Android programming : Michał Żyliński + Artur Salamon
